song.title: Whispers of the Wild
song.info:
Written for and released at Sundown 2010 in Budleigh Salterton, UK, this is probably my favorite piece of work I've done that year. It was also my first ever Demoparty visit which was a lot of fun, the song placed 7th in the newschool compo, woot! Hope you like it! :)
"SunSpire"
